{
  "page": "Port of Qarth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png/400px-HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"197\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png/600px-HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png 1.5x, /images/c/c9/HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:HBO_the_Port_of_Qarth.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The port of Qarth.</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>port of Qarth</b> is one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>'s great ports.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Port_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Horseshoe-shaped and several miles long, the port of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> is situated in a sheltered harbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Ships from the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, and the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> are permitted to dock at the far side of the harbor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The port's streets are lined with <a href=\"/index.php/Winesink\" title=\"Winesink\">winesinks</a>, warehouses, gaming dens, <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">brothels</a>, and temples. Winesinks, warehouses, and gaming dens line the streets, cheek by jowl with cheap brothels and the temples of peculiar <a href=\"/index.php/God\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God\">gods</a>. Buying and selling goes on all day and night at the waterfront marketplace, and goods might be had for a fraction of what they cost at the city's bazaar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Cutpurses, cutthroats, spellsellers, and moneychangers mingle in the crowd. Old women sell flavored waters and goat's milk from glazed ceramic jugs strapped to their shoulders. Seamen from half a hundred nations wander amongst the stalls, drinking spiced liquors and trading jokes in their languages. The air smells of salt and frying fish, of hot tar and honey, of incense and oil and sperm.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Items for sale include beautiful <a href=\"/index.php/Bronze\" title=\"Bronze\">bronze</a> daggers, <a href=\"/index.php/Brass\" title=\"Brass\">brass</a> platters, dried squids, carved <a href=\"/index.php/Onyx\" title=\"Onyx\">onyx</a>, and a magical elixir made of <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">virgin's</a> milk and <a href=\"/index.php/Shade_of_the_evening\" title=\"Shade of the evening\">shade of the evening</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_egg\" title=\"Dragon egg\">Dragon eggs</a> look suspiciously like painted rocks. Food includes honey-roasted mice and fat white cherries.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Port_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Port_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png/400px-HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"219\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png/600px-HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png 1.5x, /images/4/44/HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:HBO_Ship_in_the_Port_of_Qarth.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A ship docked at the port of Qarth.</div></div></div>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> decides to flee <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> she goes down to the docks to attempt to book ship passage to <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>. As she and her companions pass the long stone quays reserved for the ships of the <a href=\"/index.php/Thirteen\" title=\"Thirteen\">Thirteen</a>, she sees chests of saffron, frankincense, and pepper being off-loaded from <a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a>'s ornate <i><a href=\"/index.php/Vermillion_Kiss\" title=\"Vermillion Kiss\">Vermillion Kiss</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Casks of <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a>, bales of <a href=\"/index.php/Sourleaf\" title=\"Sourleaf\">sourleaf</a>, and pallets of striped hides are trundled up the gangplank onto the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Bride_in_Azure\" title=\"Bride in Azure\">Bride in Azure</a></i>, to sail on the evening tide. A crowd has gathered around the Spicer galley <i><a href=\"/index.php/Sunblaze\" title=\"Sunblaze\">Sunblaze</a></i> to bid on <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slaves</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>. At the far end of the harbor, Daenerys dismounts beside a gaming pit where a <a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk\" title=\"Basilisk\">basilisk</a> is tearing a dog to pieces amidst a shouting ring of sailors.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenerys visits various ships, including:<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Ardent_Friend\" title=\"Ardent Friend\">Ardent Friend</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Bravo_(ship)\" title=\"Bravo (ship)\">Bravo</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Faro%27s_Belly\" title=\"Lord Faro&#39;s Belly\">Lord Faro's Belly</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Magister_Manolo\" title=\"Magister Manolo\">Magister Manolo</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Pinchbottom_Petto\" title=\"Pinchbottom Petto\">Pinchbottom Petto</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Quicksilver\" title=\"Quicksilver\">Quicksilver</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Silken_Spirit\" title=\"Silken Spirit\">Silken Spirit</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Sloe-Eyed_Maid\" title=\"Sloe-Eyed Maid\">Sloe-Eyed Maid</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Trumpeteer\" title=\"Trumpeteer\">Trumpeteer</a></i></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Strong_Belwas\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Strong Belwas\">Strong Belwas</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Arstan_Whitebeard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arstan Whitebeard\">Arstan Whitebeard</a> save Daenerys from an attempt by the <a href=\"/index.php/Sorrowful_Men\" title=\"Sorrowful Men\">Sorrowful Men</a> to assassinate her with a <a href=\"/index.php/Manticore\" title=\"Manticore\">manticore</a>. Daenerys and her followers depart the port aboard <i><a href=\"/index.php/Balerion_(ship)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Balerion (ship)\">Balerion</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Meraxes_(ship)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Meraxes (ship)\">Meraxes</a></i> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar_(ship)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vhagar (ship)\">Vhagar</a></i>, intending to sail to <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Port_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> was one of the world's great ports, its great sheltered harbor a riot of color and clangor and strange smells.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Port_of_Qarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 63\">Chapter 63</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403140508\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.039 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.041 seconds\nPreprocess